Beatles - The Star-Club Tapes

This is a concise package contaning the Beatles&#039; Star-Club (Hamburg) performances in December 1962. It was sourced from several bootlegs and edited in an attempt to create a coherently sounding collection of the Star-Club tapes, albeit not being perfect. The wav files were converted to flac files for this torrent. A CUE file with proper gaps was included for use with EAC. A MD5 file and a FFP file were included for checksum purposes.

Enjoy.
